Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.93,0:00:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣舔...咳...不是啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近看啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(恭賀新禧\N今年也請多~多指教)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.84,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭賀新禧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公，今年也請多多指教~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.81,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛籤抽到上上籤，真的太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.89,0:00:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.26,0:00:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段石階，如果夫婦牽手一起走下去\N聽說老天會讓他們生小孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小...小孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.57,0:00:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起\N就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了\N也還是好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.53,0:01:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉\N也是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧.........
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一．起．來．吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.55,0:01:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自那天以來的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.19,0:01:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時都還感覺得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡都只想和你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.77,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼都好讓人心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入戀愛的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都好像魔法師一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是微不足道的小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以讓人高興起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.69,0:02:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在一起 就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被罵了 也還是好喜歡好喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一副臭臉 也是那麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.57,0:02:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 一起來吧\N一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧.........
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.57,0:02:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次一起來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「態度大變!!\N就到此為止吧!?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事之後兩個禮拜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倆人之間完全沒有進展...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謠傳各國的研究已經進入新的局面\N這個停滯的傷害可是不小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然，那個時候的震驚\N實在太大了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五歲...正是容易受傷的年齡...\N現在只有暫時靜觀其變了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.14,0:03:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C...你們到C了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，完全正確!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然、然後呢?感覺怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?那...會不會痛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?沒有那回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像飛在無邊雲端\N像是快樂得要溶化一樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.89,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到...到底是怎樣做的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎?\N還是那樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得...看起來好成熟唷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.47,0:03:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩城同學對妳很溫柔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!第一次就能引導著人家\N好高興唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次...引導...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，在那之後卻有點怪怪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪怪的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是「見內」，還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.18,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是「見外」吧...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近睡覺都跑到別的房間去睡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼?家裡鬧分居嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事吧?都到了C不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.26,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我知道了!\N岩城同學這次要莉采兒開口邀約啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.17,0:03:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由人家開口~?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯!\N一定是不想讓妳覺得被動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.67,0:04:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想等莉采兒妳\N好好提出來的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊\N老公原來是個愛害羞的人啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以更積極的對待他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~!積極~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.35,0:04:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽人家說喔...老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇哇!那、那個 嗯...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上個廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家找到老公了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!我忘了拿東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.07,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...老公...為什麼嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.24,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(把這個值代入X，這時候...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老...公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老...老師!我要去保健室一下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!等一等...呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啦~老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:05:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...不要老是做些\N動搖我心的舉動好不好啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.77,0:05:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來是以硬派出名的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可是個什麼都不知道的小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我卻隨便的反應起來\N隨著她起舞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是哪裡不對勁了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連約會都還沒有過呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家找到老公了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨、笨蛋!快住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要害羞，不要害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳住手聽到沒啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭!\N第一次纏繃帶放置不管耶~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也太天真了吧...真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉采兒，妳在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的~\N到底上哪裡去了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難...難不成...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在保健室做起來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍之介同學的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.22,0:06:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我來晚了...\N不知不覺做得太過專心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的，沒關係\N肯為我這種人做便當，我就很滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...再見了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.03,0:06:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎麼會...\N為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?聖本同學!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝妳之前的建議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的真的沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天下沒有永遠的12歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.81,0:06:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實裡，我找到了超越天使的...\N沒錯...是觀音娘娘啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我管你那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是非12歲不可?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是只愛荷包蛋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.13,0:06:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還想今後慢慢讓你\N回歸社會現實面...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-龍之介同學~!\N-嗚哇~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這大渾蛋~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是對會晃的巨乳沒辦法!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼啊~終於解開來了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(呀~!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(唧唧喳喳...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我是又怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這麼奇怪的氣氛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩城同學...岩城同學...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的...做了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?什麼做了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和莉采兒做ABC的「C」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什...什麼~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊!是誰這樣說的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰...莉采兒自己講的啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.24,0:07:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了!那件事完全是子虛烏有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼也沒能做啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說...其實是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不要胡亂推測啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，不要再給我亂散佈謠言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是大家都知道了喔\N你看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岩城同學馬上就被取了\N「色狼紀」的綽號呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要被人家這樣叫不可啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.20,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為...對啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有對啊 那傢伙真是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦~?\N要拿這個出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大剌剌的說什麼\N男人味是他的特色...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人啊，根本就是事情辦完\N馬上變個樣的隨便傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.34,0:08:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把話說的信誓旦旦...\N什麼天使!什麼觀音娘娘!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要這樣\N我也會毫不留情斬斷這段情!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可...可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼可是不可是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我說的話做，有不對過的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.09,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會變成「沒說分明都是我不對\N該做的都會做，我們和好吧!」的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要問可是該怎麼做才好，對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白，我很明白的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 照這張小抄上面的說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.97,0:08:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會絕對安全、完美無缺\N盛極必衰、風雨不斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好~去吧~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來我家...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，那傢伙到底上哪去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.33,0:08:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~真的要照這樣說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!莉采兒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.33,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:08:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...咦...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個~怎麼樣啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離...離婚協議書?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上說這說那\N結果還不是盯著巨乳不放...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這樣很丟臉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種怪人，才不會有人理你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到人家不見才發覺人家好\N那就太晚了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看...看不懂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃...呃...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家很喜歡老公\N也用自己的方式去努力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是老公你最近該怎麼說呢\N是冷淡還是不理人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.50,0:09:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者該說是躲著人家...\N總之你根本就不肯理人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是老公你本來的樣子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不像男人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.38,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不體貼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不理人、沒擔當又沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.48,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如...如果不想反省，就在這裡簽名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不講話妳就越來越大聲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊...\N一點也不了解我的心情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，夠了夠了!\N那我就如妳願幫妳簽名吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.39,0:09:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子我和妳就是陌生路人了!\N再見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.53,0:10:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...騙人的...\N怎麼會...這...樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們...離婚了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(動作快!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(雄鷹展翅了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(主啊，請賜福給我等...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(發射!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(急速下降!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.68,0:11:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什、什麼事啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.79,0:11:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈囉~達令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是穿著達令\N最愛的衣服來了唷!來~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳開什麼玩笑~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(第一次被丟耶~)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪怪?難道弄錯了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am 勒克絲\N是全球最亮眼的女孩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.11,0:11:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達令你已經離婚了對吧!\N所以啊，就和me結婚好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達令?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god!\N不過我才不讓你跑掉~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我嘛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是...美國的勒克絲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?\N為什麼突然到日本來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡~有夠纏人的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(老公，歡迎回家)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這、這是怎麼了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(老公，和我結婚吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達令的新老婆是me~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是藍蘭是也!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Net(俄語:不)!\N我蕾契兒第一斯基!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.76,0:12:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛貝莉亞!就是我了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們夠了沒有啦，一群渾蛋~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?\N為了達令，我可是日夜鍛鍊耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下!該不會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.07,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國的藍蘭、俄羅斯的蕾契兒...\N連義大利的洛貝莉亞也來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了!莉采兒人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...就在這一連串的騷動中\N完全把她追丟了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.06,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家心裡 只有老公你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.57,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是陪在人家的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.31,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起前往只有兩人的天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.59,0:13:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心兒蹦蹦跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.46,0:13:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想前去 好想前去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.46,0:13:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然人家看起來還小\N但內心已是大人了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.74,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起前往只有兩人的天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.61,0:13:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心兒蹦蹦跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.75,0:13:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了喔 要去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.62,0:13:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然人家看起來還小\N但內心已是大人了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:14:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但內心已是大人了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's cold 越來越冷了\N那就要說「凍氣」是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.78,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬梆梆的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣一冷，就擔心達令的頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要吟一首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.29,0:14:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「使君疏髮無多 妾無日不憂」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是指髮根啦(次話\N一觸即發!!美少女大亂戰)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是勒克斯\N藍蘭是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛貝莉亞唷\N蕾契兒斯基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，下一話的「爆彈小新娘」\N要講到我愛你和泡澡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有真老婆的王座...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?剛剛在說的那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這裡了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會~那就吟一首定江山吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.04,0:14:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「身處名古屋 熱水忘時燒過頭\N太燙真討厭」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是連名古屋腔都可以讓人記住的\Nnice誘人動畫是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名叫「Master Of\NEntertainment Anime」...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M.O.E!(次話\N一觸即發!!美少女大亂戰)
